OL,6,FAs part of the the force's latest , an
OL,7,Findependent scrutiny and oversight
OL,8,Fboard has been introduced which is
OL,9,Fmade up of members from black, asian
OL,10,Fand minority ethnic communities.
OL,12,FThe plan aims to better educate
OL,13,Fofficers in order to respect
OL,14,Fcommunities and eliminate racial bias.
OL,16,FThe Race Action Plan focuses on four
OL,17,Fkey areas, aiming to make minority
OL,18,Fethnic communities and colleagues feel
OL,19,Frepresented, respected, involved and
OL,20,Fprotected.
