OL,6,FAssitant Chief Constable, Dennis
OL,7,FMurray, Thames Valley Police, said:
OL,8,F"As the Chief Officer leading this
OL,9,Fvital piece of work, and being fully
OL,10,Fsupported by our Chief Constable Jason
OL,11,FHogg, I am resolute that the Race
OL,12,FAction Plan is lifted from the page
OL,13,Fand turned into demonstrable action
OL,14,Fthat improves the way we deliver
OL,15,Fpolicing services for and builds the
OL,16,Ftrust and confidence of our ethnic
OL,17,Fminority people and communities within
OL,18,Fthe Thames Valley.
