OL,6,F"Ethnic minority communities will only
OL,7,Fhave confidence to engage with us and
OL,8,Fjoin us if they are reassured that
OL,9,Fthis is not a 'tick box' exercise.
OL,11,F"I can reassure them that it is not,
OL,12,Fand delivery of the plan outcomes is
OL,13,Fessential to ensuring the culture of
OL,14,FThames Valley."
OL,16,FIn summer 2023, Thames Valley Police
OL,17,Fconducted a to inform its Race Action
OL,18,FPlan.
