OL,6,FThe Senior Responsible Officer for the
OL,7,Fnational Police Race Action Plan,
OL,8,FChief Constable Gavin Stephens, said:
OL,9,F"We have much to do to secure the
OL,10,Fconfidence of all our communities,
OL,11,Fremove discrimination, and I welcome
OL,12,Fthe news that another force have
OL,13,Flaunched their Police Race Action Plan.
OL,15,F"Taking this step is vital in making
OL,16,Fchanges needed to improve policing for
OL,17,Fblack people and shows the commitment
OL,18,FThames Valley Police has to being an
OL,19,Fanti-discriminatory police force that
OL,20,Fis trusted by everyone it serves."
